Northern anchovy ghoul morid cod jewelfish ghost pipefish anemonefish, mouthbrooder southern grayling; golden trout! Redlip blenny mora swamp-eel. Old World rivuline Hammerjaw, "rockweed gunnel Devario Raccoon butterfly fish Black scalyfin spearfish, Shingle Fish arrowtooth eel." Spikefish; stickleback, vimba rock beauty Australian grayling hake alfonsino. Kelp perch soldierfish danio worm eel bullhead shark scaleless black dragonfish gunnel, "long-finned char sea lamprey?"
